content: I buy Seed private keys  (ETH, BSC)to evm addressesPrice policy:Private (Personal) - 0.3$-10$Mix (Mixed) - 0.1$-5$The principle of working with us:(For those who have doubts, suspicions or any mistrust):Initially, you send us addresses from your seed phrases, we check them for uniqueness, then for transactions, and then for addresses that meet our conditions, you provide a seed phrase. Then we check them with the previously received addresses and pay you your profit.I will consider your addresses for purchase as a priority so that there are fewer conflict situations.I mainly buy PRIVAT, I have a lot of Mix myself and the database is constantly replenished,Therefore, do not count on a very large number of unique ones!there are topics on other forums and a lot of reviews and happy peoplefor good material they are ready to increase the price, payments are made on eth bsc in some cases btcWe also provide many different services for processing the check of your old databases.We will also help those who are subject to auto withdraw bypass, for a percentage of 30% for us, 70% for youtelegram for communicationhttps://t.me/quiz1x_seeds
